sequenceDiagram
    participant MQ as RocketMQ
    participant C as Order Consumer
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant OP as Outbox Publisher

    MQ->>C: OrderCreate(message_id, reservation_id)
    C->>PG: BEGIN
    C->>PG: INSERT consumer_inbox
    C->>PG: INSERT/LOCK inventory_reservation
    C->>PG: INSERT orders ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
    C->>PG: UPDATE sku_inventory WHERE available_stock >= 1
    C->>PG: INSERT order_items
    C->>PG: INSERT inventory_ledger
    C->>PG: UPDATE reservation PENDING_DB -> ORDERED
    C->>PG: INSERT event_outbox
    C->>PG: COMMIT
    PG-->>C: success
    C-->>MQ: ACK
    OP->>PG: claim outbox
    OP->>MQ: publish OrderCreated
    OP->>PG: mark SENT
